high_descs: Go to the long side of the white table on the right, then face the table.
Take the knife from the table that is on the bowl.
Turn left, walk to the wall, then turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Cut the lettuce in the refrigerator. Close the refrigerator door.
Stay at the refrigerator.
Put the knife on the top shelf of the refrigerator. Close the refrigerator door.
Stay at the refrigerator.
Take a piece of lettuce.
Stay at the refrigerator.
Open the freezer. Put the lettuce on the blue plate in the freezer.
Take the plate from the freezer.
Turn left and go to the white table.
Put the plate near the top left hand corner of the metal bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate with a chilled piece of lettuce on it on a table.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn right to face the white table with the head of lettuce and metal knife on it.
Pick up the large metal knife with a yellow handle off of the table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, hang a left at the oven and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and slice up the head of lettuce in the fridge, then close the fridge door.
Turn right, take a step forward then turn left to face the fridge again.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the top rack in the bottom part of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn left, take a step forward then face right so you are looking at the fridge.
Open the fridge door and pick up a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn right, take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the piece of sliced lettuce onto the blue plate.
Remove the blue plate with a piece of sliced lettuce from the fridge and close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk over to the white kitchen table.
Place the blue plate with a piece of sliced lettuce on it onto the white table behind and to the left of the deep metal pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a blue plate with a piece of sliced lettuce on it on a white table.

high_descs: Turn right and make another turn right the table on your left.
Pick up the knife only from the table.
Take to your left side and walk the knife to the fridge door.
Open and close the door with one hand.
Place the knife down in the bottom drawer.
Close the fridge door keep close to it.
Flank back on one foot to clear the way. Afterward open the fridge door.
Take out the slice of pickle only.
Swing around in place to clear the fridge door.
Open the top door of the fridge.
Take out the blue plate only in hand.
Turn left and face the table on the left.
And now drop the blue plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: This time to grab some items from the fridge.
